1.0.0.name: wordpress/tint
1.0.0.description:
Tint is a simple, yet effective tool that lets you beautifully display any social media feeds (including hashtags) from Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, Youtube, Pinterest, and RSS onto your site. Go to Tint to get yours now.

See how a few out of 10,000+ active brands are using Tint.

Where and how can YOU use Tint? Read more.

IMPORTANT: You will FIRST need to go to Tint, sign up for FREE, and create a Tint before you can embed it into your site. Check out this short video on how to properly install Tint into your Wordpress site.

If you have any questions or feedback, please email our CEO at tim{at}tintup.com.

Go to Tint to get yours now.
